d 'NTABLES': module to export journal-style publication-ready tables
d
d  ntables exports estimation and descriptive output to
d journal-formatted tables in DOCX, XLSX, HTML and CSV. It
d auto-detects the result type in memory (any e(b)/e(V) estimator,
d summary statistics, correlation matrices, cross-tabulations,
d codebooks and unit-root tests) and applies the appropriate
d layout. It supports prefix syntax, side-by-side multi-model
d regression tables, variable filtering via keep()/drop(), variable
d labels, custom significance thresholds and user-supplied notes. 
d
d KW: tables
d KW: estiaation tables
d KW: output formats 
d
d Requires: Stata version 16 (rforest from SSC required for rf option)
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260722
d
d Author: Ajay Kumar Samariya,  Noterva
d Support: email notervaindia@@gmail.com
d
f ntables.ado
f ntables.sthlp
